This file is intentionally left as a placeholder.

To enable Apple Pay on your domain, you must obtain the actual domain association file
from your Stripe dashboard:

1. Go to https://dashboard.stripe.com/settings/payment_method_domains
2. Add your domain (e.g., saltcatcharters.com and dreamlog.app)
3. Download the apple-developer-merchantid-domain-association file
4. Replace this file with the downloaded file

The file must be served at:
  https://yourdomain.com/.well-known/apple-developer-merchantid-domain-association

This path is already configured in vercel.json.
